### Phase 2 — Solidity Smart Contract + Deployment

#### [NEW] backend/contracts/LandLedger.sol
- Append-only ledger: `addRecord(string jsonPayload)` → stores `{author, timestamp, payload}`
- `getRecord(uint index)` / `recordCount()` view functions

#### [NEW] backend/scripts/deploy.ts  
- Hardhat deploy script → writes contract address to `deployments/localhost.json`

