### Phase 3 — MongoDB Models

#### [NEW] backend/src/models/User.ts
- Schema: `id` (UUID), `cnic` (unique, 13 digits), `passwordHash`, `fullName`, `email` (optional, partial unique index), `role` (enum: citizen/admin), timestamps

#### [NEW] backend/src/models/Parcel.ts
- Schema: `id` (UUID), `district`, `moza`, `plotNumber`, `khasra`, `currentOwnerCnic`, `disputed` (boolean), `ownershipHistory[]` (ownerCnic, acquiredAt, transferId, note), `hasFard`, `hasRegistry`, timestamps

#### [NEW] backend/src/models/Transfer.ts
- Schema: `id` (UUID), `parcelId`, `sellerCnic`, `buyerCnic`, `status` (pending_nadra / completed / rejected), `transactionHash`, timestamps

---

### Phase 4 — Utilities & Services

#### [NEW] backend/src/utils/cnic.ts
- `normalizeCnic(raw)` → strip non-digits, validate 13-digit length
- `isValidCnic(raw)` → boolean

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/authService.ts
- `signup(cnic, password, fullName, email?)` → hash password, create User, return public shape
- `login(cnic, password)` → verify, sign JWT with `{userId, cnic}`, return token + user
- `verifyToken(token)` → decode JWT payload

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/parcelService.ts
- `search(filters)` → AND-logic, case-insensitive regex matching for text, CNIC normalization
- `getById(id)` → single parcel or null
- `createParcel(data, fardText?, registryText?)` → save parcel + write text files to `UPLOADS_DIR`
- `getDocumentPath(parcelId, docType)` → returns filesystem path for fard/registry files

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/transferService.ts
- `initiateTransfer(sellerId, parcelId, buyerCnic)` → validates ownership, disputed check, duplicate pending check → create Transfer row
- `simulateNadra(transferId, actorUserId)` → verify actor is seller or buyer, write LAND_TRANSFER to chain, update Parcel owner + history, mark Transfer completed

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/ethLedgerService.ts
- `addRecord(jsonPayload)` → call smart contract, return txHash + recordIndex
- `getRecords()` → read all on-chain records
- `getSummary()` → recordCount, latest block, contract address, chain status

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/documentService.ts
- `generateOwnershipCertificatePdf(parcel)` → PDFKit → returns a readable stream

